<taxonomicName box="[1164,1332,1992,2021]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Habrothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="128" pageNumber="406" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hydrobates">I. hydrobates</taxonomicName>
is widely distributed across dissected mountainous terrain and includes at least three diagnosable different populations usually treated as subspecies.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
